document.title: 2019 Conference Abstracts: Annual Undergraduate Research Conference at the Interface of Biology and Mathematics

author.organization: National Institute for Mathematical and Biological Synthesis (NIMBioS)

document.abstract:
Schedule and abstract book for the Eleventh Annual Undergraduate Research Conference at the Interface of Biology and Mathematics

Date: November 16-17, 2019
Location: UT Conference Center, Knoxville
Keynote Speaker: Sadie Ryan, Medical Geography, Univ. of Florida; Director, Quantitative Disease Ecology & Conservation Lab (QDEC Lab)
Featured Speaker: Christopher Strickland, Mathematics, Univ. of Tennessee, Knoxville
